{"tid":2073534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"更多 MIJ! 日本多間大型電子廠生產線 擬撤出中國遷回日本","createTime":"2020-06-21T11:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T12:18:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"520b70e09af344080457a6999af5f45acc3d7a7c","tid":2073534,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"更多 MIJ! 日本多間大型電子廠生產線 擬撤出中國遷回日本<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sme.hket.com/article/2675406/%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%20MIJ-%20%20%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E5%BB%A0%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E7%B7%9A%20%E6%93%AC%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%B7%E5%9B%9E%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsme.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2675406%2F%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25A4%259A%2520MIJ-%2520%2520%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259E%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25B7%259A%2520%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%25B7%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=18837717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sme.hket.com/article/2675406/%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%20MIJ-%20%20%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E5%BB%A0%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E7%B7%9A%20%E6%93%AC%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%B7%E5%9B%9E%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC</a><br />\n<br />\n早前有報道指，日本計劃撥出 2,435 億日圓，以幫助日本製造商將生產轉移出中國。據日本媒體報道，日本半導體大廠羅姆 (Rohm)，以及液晶面板大廠的 JDI，正考慮將國外的製造工程，移回日本國內進行。<br />\n<br />\n據《日經新聞》報道，羅姆集中在中國及東南亞進行的後段製程，有部分可能在 2021 財年後期就會移回日本。由於生產自動化的緣故，日本國內外的成本差距已經縮小，加上新冠肺炎關係，不少工廠接連停工，所以要重新考慮供應鏈的布局。<br />\n<br />\n羅姆在近期研發出後段製程的無人化生產線，並會在今年夏天，於福岡縣的生產據點進行測試，目標在 2021 年後期進入量產。公司社長松本功表示，如果有了無人化或省人化產線，國內生產就有辦法獲利，表明公司正考慮將生產線移回日本。<br />\n<br />\nJDI 的菊岡稔社長表示，自動化後製的投資正在進行，指日本國內的勞動成本差異，並沒有這麼大，而且前段製程與後段製程，若是都在同一地區，材料的運輸成本也會下降。<br />\n<br />\n村田製作所執行董事中島規巨亦指出，日本國內生産會成為一個優勢，並非處於一味遷往海外的局面。"},{"pid":"1f58ad86555e31d69fbec2b6ff46ef8325053c54","tid":2073534,"uid":45358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"擬"},{"pid":"58511f2ae0619a18b4dd84d510e0904004924063","tid":2073534,"uid":264529,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:52:17.000Z","msg":"到時MIJ平過MIC <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569c30f2f523afdcabb4d6277f8ec66ac436a393","tid":2073534,"uid":266342,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"MIJ 品質保證<br />\nMIC(MIZ) 垃圾"},{"pid":"a5b3f95f44e31916e2b7fc5b502810f29af85614","tid":2073534,"uid":60635,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"MIJ咪又係請越南人去生產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0753d8171685cba48854c1acde0c14862ab9b766","tid":2073534,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:56:37.000Z","msg":"Anywhere but Chi na"},{"pid":"d11594e19454e4f53db5b0bbebdde83e2055f942","tid":2073534,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"剛剛FB 又話 松下 打算係中国開新廠。"},{"pid":"637c4fc4d4d10c3f2419977cdd1edfc732f39760","tid":2073534,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />MORE!MORE!"},{"pid":"d5995395d90cad67f4cace8484ce1695b45265c6","tid":2073534,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d11594e19454e4f53db5b0bbebdde83e2055f942","tid":2073534,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"剛剛FB 又話 松下 打算係中国開新廠。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"鬼咩Panasonic而家都唔係松下家話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor